	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>82 Beam St</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N Y.</placeName> <date>Mch 21&#47;65</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Rev&#58; I Leeser</addressee>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)" >Dear sir and friend.</p>
				<p>I had the <add>&#63;</add> &#8220;Matzot&#8221;<lb/> shipped in the &#8220;Arage&#8221; yesterday PM&#44;<lb/> and ordered the 3000 A baked<lb/> here to be shipped to day.</p>
				<p>I could not obtain Transportation<lb/> until yesterday afternoon for <add>&#63;</add><lb/> <persName>Van Vlick</persName>.  I think it will be<lb/> needless to have them insured.<lb/>  I shall see this evening if all<lb/> were shipped properly and will write<lb/> you again to <add>&#63;</add>.  I should <del>like</del><lb/> like to have you send this week<lb/> to <placeName>441 North 5th St</placeName> for me&#44; a copy<lb/> of each of the Books you may have<lb/> suitable for Religious instruction&#44;<lb/> Your Catechism&#44; <persName>Pikes</persName>&#44; <persName>Peixottos</persName> <add>&#63;</add><lb/> and the price per Dozen&#59; I want</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>them for the consideration of the<lb/> Board of the Hebrew Free School of<lb/> this city.  With kind regards</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">Very truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">M. M. Allen</persName>.</p>
				<p>I will furnish you with a list<lb/> of the Donors to the <placeName>Savannah</placeName> fund<lb/> for your &#8220;Occident&#8221; if you wish it.</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">M.</persName></p>
		</body>
